<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Marsa Imbarak</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/marsalam/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Marsa Imbarak</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        O excursie de toata ziua din Portul Ghalib catre faimoasele gradini Marsa Imbarakreef cu broaste testoate si multe specii de pesti.
        Atracția incontestabilă are o sansă mare sa vedeti DUGONG în mediul său natural! Este un loc pe care trebuie vazut!
        Pranzul pe barca si bauturi non alcoolice sunt incluse. Echipamentul pentru snorkeling (masca,tub,inotatoare) sunt gratis
        Sosirea la hotel la ora 17:00-17:30
        <br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        luni si vineri
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        A whole day excursion from Port Ghalib to very famous Marsa Imbarak reef gardens with sea turtles and 
        many various fish. Unquestionable attraction is a high chance to see a DUGONG in its natural enviroment! 
        It is a must see place! Lunch on the boat and non alcoholic drinks included. Snorekling equipment 
        (mask,pipe,feence) available for free. Arrival to hotel at 17:00-17:30
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        Monday and Friday
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>